---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="トップ">
  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h1><span><Icon name="line-md:compass" /></span>物理部展2024</h1>
        <p>
          第77回栄光祭催し物「物理部展2024」の特設ページです。物理部展の情報や物理部の活動を紹介しています。<br
          />栄光学園校舎の北棟で開催されます。ぜひお越しください！
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <a
          class="twitter-timeline"
          data-height="500"
          data-lang="ja"
          data-theme="light"
          href="https://twitter.com/EikoPhysicsClub?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"
          >@EikoPhysicsClubのポストを読み込み中...</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
<script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"
></script>
<style lang="scss">
  main {
    .container {
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      margin-inline: auto;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      .content {
        flex: 1;
        &:first-child {
          filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px #fefeff) drop-shadow(0 0 10px #fefeff)
            drop-shadow(0 0 10px #fefeff);
          padding: 1rem;
          h1 {
            border-bottom: 3px solid #29009b;
            span {
              // 文字の高さ変更
              display: inline-block;
              transform: translateY(0.15em);
            }
          }
        }
        &:last-child {
          .twitter-timeline {
            font-size: 17px;
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
</style>
<style is:global>
  .twitter-timeline > iframe {
    width: 100% !important;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
</style>
